//Maximum letter for imgData is P.
let imgData = ["ABCD", "EFGH", "IJKL", "MNOP"]
//Does nothing, this variable is overwritten in the end.
const PAssist = {
    cursorPos: {
        x: 0,
        y: 0
    },
    anchorPoint: {
        x: 0,
        y: 0
    },
    colorAssist: true,
    palette: document.getElementById("colors").children,
    observer: new MutationObserver(function(mut) {
        const posstr = mut[0].target.data.replace(/\(|\)/g, "").split(",")
          , cpos = PAssist.cursorPos
          , apos = PAssist.anchorPoint;
        cpos.x = parseInt(posstr[0])
        cpos.y = parseInt(posstr[1])
        const color = PAssist.getPixelColor(cpos.x - apos.x, cpos.y - apos.y)
        PAssist.colorCheck.style.visibility = typeof (color) === "number" ? "hidden" : "visible";
        if (!PAssist.colorAssist) {
            return
        }
        typeof (color) === "number" && !PAssist.palette[color].className && PAssist.palette[color].click()
    }
    ),
    getPixelColor: function(x, y) {
        if (x < 0 || y < 0) {
            return
        }
        if (y < imgData.length && x < imgData[0].length) {
            let color = imgData[y].charCodeAt(x) - 65
            if (color > 15) {
                return
            }
            return color
        }
    },
    setAnchor: function(x, y) {
        this.anchorPoint.x = x
        this.anchorPoint.y = y
        this.anchorText.innerText = "Anchor Point:" + x + "; " + y
        this.dispatch(this.webpack_modules[48].exports.m([x, y])); // setView to the anchor point and let it load chunks
        this.dispatch(this.webpack_modules[48].exports.n(1)); // setScale to zoom all the way out and load more chunks
    },
    colorCheck: document.createElement("DIV"),
    anchorText: document.createElement("DIV"),
    initialize: function() {
        let webpack_modules;
        webpackJsonp([], {
          69420: function(a, b, require) {
            webpack_modules = require.c;
          }
        }, [69420]);
        this.webpack_modules = webpack_modules;
        delete webpack_modules[69420];

        const cc = this.colorCheck
          , ccs = cc.style
          , at = this.anchorText
          , ats = at.style
        document.getElementById("app").children[0].appendChild(cc)
        cc.innerText = "No defined color for this pixel"
        ccs.position = "absolute"
        ccs.left = "1em"
        ccs.top = "11em"
        ccs.color = "red"
        ccs.visibility = "hidden"
        ccs.background = "white"
        document.getElementById("app").children[0].appendChild(at)
        at.innerText = "Anchor Point:" + this.anchorPoint.x + "; " + this.anchorPoint.y
        ats.position = "absolute"
        ats.left = "1em"
        ats.top = "8em"
        ats.background = "white"

        const reactroot = document.querySelector("div[data-reactroot]")
        for (let i in reactroot) {
            if (i.includes("__react")) {
                this.dispatch = reactroot[i]._renderedChildren[".a"]._context.store.dispatch
                this.getState = reactroot[i]._renderedChildren[".a"]._context.store.getState
                this.waitDiv = reactroot[i]._renderedChildren[".3"]._renderedComponent._renderedComponent._renderedComponent._hostNode
                break
            }
        }
        this.updateDimensions()
    },
    placePixel: function(x, y) {
        let col = this.getPixelColor(x - this.anchorPoint.x, y - PAssist.anchorPoint.y);
        let chunkId = [x,y].map(x => Math.floor(x / 64)).join(":");
        let cx = x - (Math.floor(x/64) * 64);
        let cy = y - (Math.floor(y/64) * 64);
        let skip = this.getState().canvas.chunks.get(chunkId).hasColorIn([cx,cy], col);
        if (typeof (col) === "number" && !skip) {
            console.log("placePixel: ", chunkId, x, y);
            this.dispatch(this.webpack_modules[48].exports.m([x, y])); // setView
            this.dispatch(this.webpack_modules[48].exports.x([x, y], col)); // requestPlacePixel
            return true
        }
        return false
    },
    isWaiting: function() {
        return this.waitDiv.style.display === "block"
    },
    startBot: function() {
        if (!this.dispatch || !this.webpack_modules) {
            console.error("Failed to initialize");
            return false
        }
        this.colorAssist = true
        this.botfn(this)
        !this.botId && (this.botId = setInterval(this.botfn, 3000, this))
    },
    botfn: function(a) {
        if (a.isWaiting()) {
            return false
        }
        let i = 0
        while (!a.placePixel(a.botCoords.x + a.anchorPoint.x, a.botCoords.y + a.anchorPoint.y)) {
            a.botCoords.x++
            if (a.botCoords.x > a.imgDim.width) {
                a.botCoords.x = 0
                a.botCoords.y++
            }
            if (a.botCoords.y > a.imgDim.height) {
                a.botCoords.x = 0
                a.botCoords.y = 0
                break
            }
            i++
            if (i > 2048) {
                console.log("No color painted in this scan, trying again in 3 seconds. x: " + a.botCoords.x + "; y: " + a.botCoords.y)
                break
            }
        }
    },
    disableBot: function() {
        clearInterval(this.botId)
        this.botId = undefined;
    },
    botCoords: {
        x: 0,
        y: 0
    },
    imgDim: {
        width: 0,
        height: 0
    },
    updateDimensions: function() {
        this.imgDim.width = imgData[0].length
        this.imgDim.height = imgData.length
    }
}
PAssist.observer.observe(document.querySelector('div[style="position: absolute; left: 1em; bottom: 1em;"]').children[0], {
    characterData: true,
    subtree: true
})
